# Name

furniture discount

## Description

On this website users can get a discount on some brand furnitures.
Users just need to copy the discount code of the chosen furniture and 
give it at the brick-and-mortar store.

Furniture sellers that want to give discount on some of their brand furnitures - 
just need to sign up in the website and publish their furnitures.

## Getting Started

If you are a user that want to get a discount on some brand furnitures - 
you do not need to register. Just copy the discount code of the chosen furniture
and give it at the brick-and-mortar store.

If you are a furniture seller - you need to sign up in the website and 
publish your furnitures.

## Roadmap

I would like to improve this website to a professional level after several months.

